            "title": "西甲｜巴塞隆拿涉違規派球員上陣 奧沙辛拿正式提告 罪成或判輸波",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"巴塞隆拿中堅恩尼高馬天尼斯。Getty\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/760fa4f5a6b9c6e77bc12a2f5bfa7c6f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250329/_2025032913585846962.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">巴塞隆拿中堅恩尼高馬天尼斯。Getty</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>巴塞隆拿於周四西甲主場3:0擊敗奧沙辛拿，後者於周五發官方聲明表示已向西班牙足總上訴，指控巴塞該仗違規派中堅恩尼高馬天尼斯上陣，而根據條例，一旦巴塞罪成，該仗將會被改判輸波。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"巴塞隆拿中堅恩尼高馬天尼斯。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f8456a5e7ef52aefea955277dbbbb29e/2025-03/GettyImages-2204707206.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        巴塞隆拿中堅恩尼高馬天尼斯。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"巴塞隆拿中堅恩尼高馬天尼斯。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4015a2afad691ba162452f1edb5e4a6f/2025-03/GettyImages-2180632874.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        巴塞隆拿中堅恩尼高馬天尼斯。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"巴塞隆拿中堅恩尼高馬天尼斯(右)。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ccb26eeb959e2c08eea6b8c8a86310a5/2025-03/GettyImages-2207229531.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        巴塞隆拿中堅恩尼高馬天尼斯(右)。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"巴塞隆拿中堅恩尼高馬天尼斯。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cec73189693ffe97ecd066b1a4bd81a1/2025-03/GettyImages-2180632835.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        巴塞隆拿中堅恩尼高馬天尼斯。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"巴塞隆拿擊敗奧沙辛拿。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/54925c3a562827f299401ad4e659c626/2025-03/GettyImages-2207242130.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        巴塞隆拿擊敗奧沙辛拿。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"巴塞隆拿擊敗奧沙辛拿。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/98bb41d82c1c2b19d716c255629e4739/2025-03/GettyImages-2207242022.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        巴塞隆拿擊敗奧沙辛拿。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"巴塞隆拿擊敗奧沙辛拿。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/51763051be97db913dbbf25a6658b187/2025-03/GettyImages-2207231372.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        巴塞隆拿擊敗奧沙辛拿。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>巴塞涉違規派球員上陣</h2>\n<p>恩尼高馬天尼斯因右膝傷患於剛過去的國際賽期退出西班牙國家隊，未有隨隊出戰歐國聯賽事。而根據國際足協規定，因傷退出國家隊的球員，在國際賽期結束後5天內不能為球會上陣，但馬天尼斯於周四卻為巴塞上陣更踢足全場，而這場比賽與西班牙對荷蘭的比賽只隔了4天，故有違規之嫌。\n\n</p><h2>罪成或判輸波</h2>\n<p>奧沙辛拿在聲明中指出：「我們相信因傷退出國家隊的馬天尼斯違反了國際足協規定，不符合周四西甲上陣的資格。我們決定正式提出控告。」而根據西班牙足總規定，如果球會派出不符上陣資格的球員，應被判棄權，對手直接獲勝。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2060926/即時-體育-西甲-巴塞隆拿涉違規派球員上陣-奧沙辛拿正式提告-罪成或判輸波",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-29 14:01:21",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "珍惜生命｜長沙灣女子山坡吊頸亡",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/1e170c2b0ebb39862bd7733e4a4a4837/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250329/_2025032913540826670.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今(29日)晨上11時17分，有行山人士途經長沙灣大埔公路琵琶山段近長源路一座已荒廢警察宿舍對開樹林，發現一名年約50歲女子在山坡上一棵大樹吊頸，大驚報警。消防到場將事主解下，當場證實已氣絕身亡，警方正調查死者身份及輕生原因。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4165147/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方在場調查。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7c71473560ba1d81c9448ac4089a9f1c/2025-03/01_1_32.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方在場調查。楊偉亨攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4165148/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方在場調查。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/05c088ffa64948318e23eb6cc7b0fc92/2025-03/02_0_14.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__