            "title": "上水狗隻高處墮下  重傷奄奄一息",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"狗隻高處墮下重傷。fb：上水人大聯盟\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a961f81d6ea3a3d40d758eae42772f43/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250329/_2025032913344321297.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">狗隻高處墮下重傷。fb：上水人大聯盟</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>上水發生「墮狗」事件，今（29日）中午12時26分，上水清曉路1號清濤苑一隻狗從高處墮下，倒臥商場對開馬路，重創吐血奄奄一息，男子大驚報警，警方在場調查，初步懷疑從5樓平台墮下，因該狗頸脖有狗套，懷疑有人飼養，正聯絡狗主及調查墮樓原因，同時通知愛協人員。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4165123/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"狗隻高處墮下重傷。fb：上水人大聯盟\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/745903eec76bada8a74385e16e7ad091/2025-03/01_1_31.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        狗隻高處墮下重傷。fb：上水人大聯盟\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4165124/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"狗隻高處墮下重傷。fb：上水人大聯盟\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ae39e0c4b1d2fe4f14dda88e89fbfbb8/2025-03/02_1_30.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        狗隻高處墮下重傷。fb：上水人大聯盟\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4165125/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"狗隻重傷奄奄一息。fb：上水人大聯盟\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b2c9b9b3ac011241f04f2958940cef16/2025-03/03_2_23.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        狗隻重傷奄奄一息。fb：上水人大聯盟\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4165126/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"區議員劉鎮海在場了解。fb：上水人大聯盟\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8e4450211d9e54e6d0b3f5b0d3bfebee/2025-03/04_1_19.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        區議員劉鎮海在場了解。fb：上水人大聯盟\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4165127/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方在場調查。fb：上水人大聯盟\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cd8e458fdcb5451d2e87f98e98517fdf/2025-03/05_1_23.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方在場調查。fb：上水人大聯盟\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
